title: Data Type
text: All of the data for the three people is the same kind, and can be classified together as data about age.

title: Data in a Row
text: Data in a row corresponds with all of the attribute values collected from one $$\frac{object}{person}$$

title: Data in a Table
text: There is not enough data attributes collected for each person to create a full table.

title: Purpose of a Schema
text: A schema is made to show the relationship between tables and is made of multiple tables with significant amounts of data for each person.
